# Hardened SSH Configuration for Vast.ai Container

# Listen on all interfaces for health checks and external connections.
ListenAddress 0.0.0.0
ListenAddress ::

# THE FIX: Explicitly enable TCP Forwarding for VS Code Remote-SSH.
AllowTcpForwarding yes

# Standard and hardened settings
Port 22
Protocol 2
PermitRootLogin yes
UsePAM yes
PasswordAuthentication no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
X11Forwarding no
AllowAgentForwarding no
LogLevel VERBOSE
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server